data.description: Priced to sell NOW!!! Just 8 minutes away from Miami's desirable Wynwood. Nicely renovated 4 bedroom 3 bath single family home. Home is much bigger than tax rolls state. Bonus 4th bedroom has it's own entrance! A perfect in law quarters. This lovely home with it's oversized lot is nestled on a quiet tree lined street just minutes away from South Beach and with no HOA This awesome home has the ability to be an Air B&B or a traditional rental or for the large family it has plenty of space for a family member to have their own space. This house is a diamond. Hurry, this one will not last!!!
